tldr: The user requested a review of the sleep questionnaire application against
  the provided specifications and a subsequent implementation of missing
  features. The agent successfully implemented a tiredness severity scale,
  COMISA detection, insufficient sleep syndrome detection, outbound resource
  links, weighted EDS scoring, expanded CSV export, and chronic fatigue
